# Elior Novan - Personal Website

This is the personal website for Eric Makau (Elior Novan), an upcoming Kenyan author exploring science in technology and human connections to nature.

## Live Website
[https://yourusername.github.io/elior-novan-website](https://yourusername.github.io/elior-novan-website)

## Features
- Responsive design for all devices
- Modern, nature-inspired color scheme
- Social media integration
- Direct contact information
- Smooth scrolling navigation
- Interactive elements

## Setup for GitHub Pages

1. **Create a GitHub repository** named `elior-novan-website`

2. **Upload all files** to the repository:
   - `index.html`
   - `style.css`
   - `script.js`
   - `README.md`
   - Create `assets/images/` folder and add your profile picture as `profile.jpg`

3. **Enable GitHub Pages**:
   - Go to repository Settings
   - Click on "Pages" in the sidebar
   - Under "Source", select "main" branch
   - Click "Save"
   - Your site will be published at `https://yourusername.github.io/elior-novan-website`

4. **Customize**:
   - Replace `yourusername` with your actual GitHub username
   - Update social media links with your actual profile URLs
   - Add your profile image to `assets/images/profile.jpg`

